verses.roman:
jaya jaya śrī-caitanya svayaṁ bhagavān
jaya jaya gauracandra bhakta-gaṇa-prāṇa

synonyms: jaya jaya—all glories; śrī-caitanya—to Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu; svayam bhagavān—the Personality of Godhead Himself; jaya jaya—all glories; gaura-candra—to Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu; bhakta-gaṇa-prāṇa—the life and soul of the devotees.
translation: All glories to Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu, the Supreme Personality of Godhead! All glories to Lord Gauracandra, the life and soul of His devotees.
